parcel.description: Community Space for music, art and events.

features.text:
# Tempest

Everyone of us have a certain turmoil bubbling within us, it can take the littlest of winds to start the greatest storms. That’s why this work represented by the bold colors and the unsettling pose of the four models denotes the imbalance that threatens to swallow us whole when we give in to the “TEMPEST”

Collab:
Nirvan x Dagapa

# 112 Meals

A little experience I had with a Club from Tangier : Rotaract Tanger Doyen - A night they decided to feed the homeless.

swisster
H E A D S P A C E

5 Leda is a communally owned experimental space founded by active users of Cent.

9 months ago, these community members pooled together, trusted each other and committed to showcasing lesser-known artists and work with real-world impact.

We're happy to welcome you to HEADSPACE, featuring mindblowing art by:

sphericalart . nirvan . Eli Jayne . Legendary Fame . Erick Stowe

Downstairs includes work by:

ufhouck . swisster . indefatigable
